%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49648bcba4377fb359d3030aae97f70274ca6224","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"我要831真相！！！"},{"pid":"b8f98ad68a7dd8f520e314ff8da2ff24d918eab6","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人帶走！！！<br />\n<br />\n依加好多重要事件，但一定要分先後！！"},{"pid":"e7f6e0559863bdd3ef34760da7aa20ef1dc1652b","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推啊！！！！"},{"pid":"08613f2b1a3a1b177b6929ac923a367916691714","tid":1544842,"uid":186276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"40b8cb6786c6d271d3ce0921440afbd4a62003f1","tid":1544842,"uid":162765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bccfa446eb9a69a2d3a325a15816af29215af460","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"推啊！！！！！"},{"pid":"bf5bc69661e806ed9bd3608641f5222d84beca18","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"我要831真相"},{"pid":"ff9d1d8a2ad63e48376c368cc7d9c58ec60a5d38","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記太子站嘅手足！！"},{"pid":"b14ae64153c628fb483cc939ca4128e65c7a7a24","tid":1544842,"uid":39555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:48:00.000Z","msg":"佢地等緊還原真相！！"},{"pid":"99ad45364f45c64dd86ee